\ Scalar/matrix broadcasting through the polymorphic + - * / primitives.
[ 1 2 3 4 ] 2 2 matrix 10 + .
[ 10 20 30 40 ] 2 2 matrix 5 - .
[ 1 2 3 4 ] 2 2 matrix 3 * .
[ 10 20 30 40 ] 2 2 matrix 10 / .
[ 1 2 ] 1 2 matrix 0 + .
[ 1 2 3 ] 1 3 matrix 0 * .
\ scalar on the left broadcasts too
10 [ 1 2 3 4 ] 2 2 matrix + .
100 [ 10 20 30 40 ] 2 2 matrix - .
